Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllPtnCuts(25.10)                                deleteAllPtnCuts(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllPtnCuts - Deletes all the partition cuts in the floorplan

Syntax
        deleteAllPtnCuts

       [-help]

       Deletes  all the partition cuts in the floorplan. You can use this com-
       mand after specifying a partition.

       Note: Command deleteAllPtnCuts is now obsolete and will be  removed  in
       the  next major release of the software. This command has been replaced
       by the deletePtnCut command.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the deleteAllPtnCuts command. For
              a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteAllPtnCuts

Related Information
              * partition

              * deletePtnCut

              * deletePartition

              * Partitioning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

